      • cellByDirectIndex

        public void cellByDirectIndex(int index,
                              double value)
        Set a cell value by the index in the internal layout of this cell. This requires knowledge of the internal layout of cells in this implementation, and should therefore probably not be used (but when it can be used it is fast).
